  <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" role="paragraph" id="par_id3145383" l10n="U" oldref="192">The search criteria for attributes are listed below the <emph>Search for</emph> box.</paragraph>
  <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" role="note" id="par_id3150466" l10n="U" oldref="132">You do not need to specify a search text in the <emph>Search for</emph> box when you search and replace formatting.</paragraph>
  <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" oldref="133" role="paragraph" id="par_id3156152" l10n="U">To define a replacement format, click in the <emph>Replace with</emph> box, and then click the <emph>Format </emph>button.</paragraph>
  <paragraph xml-lang="en-US" oldref="157" role="paragraph" id="par_id3153821" l10n="U">Use the <emph>Text Format (Search)</emph> or the <emph>Text Format (Replace)</emph> to define your formatting search criteria. These dialogs contain the following tab pages:</paragraph>
